Scaffolding (README, workflow yml): MIT.

Data (`data/`): each cloud's IP range publication carries its own terms.
  - AWS ip-ranges.json — https://docs.aws.amazon.com/vpc/latest/userguide/aws-ip-ranges.html
  - Azure ServiceTags — https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=56519
  - GCP cloud.json   — https://cloud.google.com/vpc/docs/subnets
  - Cloudflare IPs    — https://www.cloudflare.com/ips/

Review each provider's terms before redistribution.
